show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/CVKrnZ
show.description: In a decaying mental asylum, Tushita dies in front of her little daughter Abhira, leaving behind a box of letters revealing a heartbreaking story of betrayal, lost love, and stolen identity. When Varun, her estranged husband, finally learns the truth, he finds his real daughter replaced by the scheming women Sambhavna. Tushita reveals Sambhavna' s dark intensions by coming as twin sister of Tushita. Watch "Revenge in Second Life" now.
